        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This handsome tassel comes in a variety of colors to match your companion's collar or bridle. While attached, the tassel gives the companion a +1 item bonus to Acrobatics checks to Balance, and to their Reflex DC against Trip attacks.",
